"remains in office for the entire duration of the project, until the "
"conclusion of the activities provided for therein. The appointment is unpaid."

#: parco_verismo/templates/parco_verismo/comitato_regolamento.html:87
msgid "Art. 4 – Compiti e funzioni"
msgstr "Art. 4 – Tasks and functions"

